---
title: cells_and_kzg_proofs_construction (fulu-validator)
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB

    [*] --> q_init : start
    q_init --> q_iter : cells_and_kzg_proofs = []
    q_iter --> q_start : for i, blob in enumerate(blobs_bundle.blobs)
    q_start --> q_end : start = i * CELLS_PER_EXT_BLOB
    q_end --> q_zip : end = (i + 1) * CELLS_PER_EXT_BLOB
    q_zip --> q_extend : cell_proofs = zip(compute_cells(blob), blobs_bundle.proofs[start:end])
    q_extend --> q_iter : cells_and_kzg_proofs.extend(cell_proofs)
    q_iter --> [*] : no more blobs

    note right of q_zip
        INV: Each blob produces exactly CELLS_PER_EXT_BLOB cell-proof pairs
        INV: blobs_bundle.proofs has length CELLS_PER_EXT_BLOB * len(blobs_bundle.blobs)
        INV: Proof slicing indices [start:end] are always in bounds
    end note
